item.title: Turkey raises death toll to 33 troops in Syrian airstrike
item.description: ANKARA, Turkey (AP) — Turkey on Friday raised the loss of life toll from a Syrian authorities airstrike on its forces in northwestern Syria the outdated night to 33 Turkish troops, the ideal number of Turkish troopers killed in a single day since Ankara first intervened within the Syrian battle in 2016.
